The path that you see on the map on satellite view can be a little difficult to follow and will lead you through farms and even a cow pasture. We don’t personally know the whole trail. However, if you want to take it you will enjoy the view of the farm land and see more of the country side.

Where to park your car

There are two places to park your car in this area. The first is the small parking lot that is shown on the map, but there is more parking at the bottom of the map on the other side of the river. If you park at the first location be prepared to hike up the hill. However, when you have to turn a tight corner, just head up the hill on the far right side rather than taking a shorter turn in. It will be easier to get into the street this way.

Besides the parking options, the area is quite deserted so you’ll likely be alone as you walk around and explore. Enjoy Montenegro!
